        "title": "Failure: org.apache.maven plugins:maven-jar-plugin:2.6:test-jar",
        "body": "<p>I'm trying to compile a project but I'm running into a Maven plugin error. <\/p>\n\n<p>I use Apache Maven 3.3.9 and <code>java-9-openjdk<\/code>, with the command<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn clean install -DskipTests=true\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>but that fails with the following message:<\/p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Error: Failed to execute goal org.apache.maven plugins:maven-jar-plugin:2.6:test-jar<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>Do I have to modify my pom file?<\/p>\n\n<pre><code> &lt;build&gt;\n    &lt;plugins&gt;\n      &lt;plugin&gt;\n        &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n        &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-deploy-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n        &lt;configuration&gt;\n          &lt;skip&gt;true&lt;/skip&gt;\n        &lt;/configuration&gt;\n      &lt;/plugin&gt;\n      &lt;plugin&gt;\n        &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n        &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-install-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n        &lt;configuration&gt;\n          &lt;skip&gt;true&lt;/skip&gt;\n        &lt;/configuration&gt;\n      &lt;/plugin&gt;\n      &lt;plugin&gt;\n        &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n        &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n        &lt;configuration&gt;\n          &lt;sourcepath&gt;*/target/generated-sources/mdsal-binding/*&lt;/sourcepath&gt;\n          &lt;excludePackageNames&gt;*&lt;/excludePackageNames&gt;\n        &lt;/configuration&gt;\n      &lt;/plugin&gt;\n    &lt;/plugins&gt;\n  &lt;/build&gt;\n&lt;/project&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
