            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1539677231,
            "creation_date": 1539677231,
            "body": "<p>Based on the mention of <code>mdsal-binding<\/code> in your POM, you\u2019re trying to build an <a href=\"https://www.opendaylight.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">OpenDaylight<\/a> project (I\u2019m guessing either <code>coretutorials<\/code> or <code>transportpce<\/code>) with JDK 9. We don\u2019t support that yet; you must build with JDK 8.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 52838397,
            "question_id": 52838395
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://graph.facebook.com/10153705028107521/picture?type=large",
                "account_id": 7405566,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 5634603,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5634603/vasanth-saminathan",
                "reputation": 605,
                "display_name": "Vasanth Saminathan"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1545647609,
            "creation_date": 1545647609,
            "body": "<p>Since you are using <strong>-DskipTests=true<\/strong> it is trying to avoid test.\nThat subsequently fails to generate the test-jar.<\/p>\n\n<p>Either you could comment out the <strong><em>test jar goal<\/em><\/strong>.\nElse do not skip the tests.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 53912224,
            "question_id": 52838395
        }
